case is useful for multiple-choice conditions.

Syntax:

case $variable in
  pattern1) commands ;;
  pattern2) commands ;;
  *) default ;;
esac


Example:

echo "Enter a fruit:"
read fruit
case $fruit in
  apple) echo "You chose apple." ;;
  banana) echo "You chose banana." ;;
  *) echo "Unknown fruit." ;;
esac
